com.walmart.qe.mobilebot.service

Class DeviceService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.walmart.qe.mobilebot.service.DeviceService

  • @Service
public class DeviceService
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all methods required to work with a device You can create, read, update, delete devices, as well as interact with physical devices using these methods.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Adam Burns (a2burns)
